      "content": "hey, i'm looking at the dashboard for the 'AeroPeak Running Shoes' and the stock counts look pretty thin for the next few weeks. we're supposed to be pushing these hard for the summer promo. should we just mark them as 'out of stock' now so we dont have people ordering stuff we cant ship, or keep them live?",
